title: HEADHUNTERS Ep3: Melbourne Near Miss
description: Episode 3 of our special podcast series looking back at the epic 1974/5 Ashes fifty years ago. This programme features the Boxing Day Test in Melbourne 1974 in which all results were possible until the very end. Dennis Amiss and Ian Chappell help Simon Hughes and Simon Mann tell the story. For the complete series go to patreon.com/theanalyst25 Learn more about your ad choices. Visit podcastchoices.com/adchoices
author: Simon Hughes
